PATTERNS
## Example inflection pattern:
# NounRoot RegNounInfl
Animate-Nouns
Inanimate-Nouns
Intransitive-Verbs
Transitive-Verbs

PATTERN Animate-Nouns
:Animate-N-Infl(1)? Animate-N-Stems [<n><aa>:] Animate-N-Infl(2)? 

PATTERN Inanimate-Nouns
:Inanimate-N-Infl(1)? Inanimate-N-Stems [<n><nn>:] Inanimate-N-Infl(2)?

PATTERN Intransitive-Verbs
:Intransitive-V-Infl(1)? Intransitive-V-Stems [<v><iv>:] Intransitive-V-Infl(2)?

PATTERN Transitive-Verbs
:Transitive-V-Infl(1)? Transitive-V-Stems [<v><tv>:] Transitive-V-Infl(2)?

LEXICON Animate-N-Infl(2)
:    <pl>:>ak
:{N}{t}{U}> <px1sg>:>um #Dir/LR
:{N}{t}{U}> <px1sg>:
:k{t}{U}> <px2sg>:>um #Dir/LR
:k{t}{U}> <px2sg>:
:w{t}{U}> <px3sg>:>um #Dir/LR    
:w{t}{U}> <px3sg>:   
:n{t}{U}> <px1pl>:>um>una #Dir/LR
:n{t}{U}> <px1pl>:>una
:{N}{t}{U}> <px2pl>:>um>uwa #Dir/LR
:{N}{t}{U}> <px2pl>:>uwa
:k{t}{U}> <px3pl>:>um>uwaawal #Dir/LR
:k{t}{U}> <px3pl>:>uwaawal
:{N}{t}{U}> <px1sg><pl>:>um>ak #Dir/LR
:{N}{t}{U}> <px1sg><pl>:>ak
:k{t}{U}> <px2sg><pl>:>um>ak #Dir/LR
:k{t}{U}> <px2sg><pl>:>ak
:w{t}{U}> <px3sg><pl>:um>al #Dir/LR
:w{t}{U}> <px3sg><pl>:>al    


LEXICON Inanimate-N-Infl(2)
:    <pl>:>al
:{N}{t}{U}> <px1sg>:>um #Dir/LR
:{N}{t}{U}> <px1sg>:
:k{t}{U}> <px2sg>:>um #Dir/LR
:k{t}{U}> <px2sg>:
:w{t}{U}> <px3sg>:>um #Dir/LR
:w{t}{U}> <px3sg>:>   
:w{t}{U}> <px1pl>:>um>una #Dir/LR
:w{t}{U}> <px1pl>:>una
:{N}{t}{U}> <px2pl>:>um>uwa #Dir/LR
:{N}{t}{U}> <px2pl>:>uwa
:k{t}{U}> <px3pl>:>um>uwaawal #Dir/LR
:k{t}{U}> <px3pl>:>uwaawal
:{N}{t}{U}> <px1sg><pl>:>um>al #Dir/LR
:{N}{t}{U}> <px1sg><pl>:>al
:k{t}{U}> <px2sg><pl>:>um>al #Dir/LR
:k{t}{U}> <px2sg><pl>:>al
:w{t}{U}> <px3sg><pl>:>um>uwa #Dir/LR
:w{t}{U}> <px3sg><pl>:>uwa 


LEXICON Intransitive-V-Infl(2)

# Intransitive Inanimate Verbs
:    <nn><s_sg>:>w
:    <nn><s_pl>:>wal

# Intransitive Animate Verbs
:n{u}> <aa><s_1sg>:>{m}
:k{u}> <aa><s_2sg>:>{m}
:   <aa><s_3sg>:>{w}     
:{n}{k}{u}> <aa><s_1pl>:>ohna
:k{u}> <aa><s_2pl>:>ohmwa
:   <aa><s_3pl>:>ook
:   <aa><s_3pl>:>{w}a>k


LEXICON Transitive-V-Infl(2)

# Transitive Inanimate Verbs w/ Singular Object
:n{u}> <nn><s_1sg><o_sg>:>{u}n
:k{u}> <nn><s_2sg><o_sg>:>{u}n
:w{u}> <nn><s_3sg><o_sg>:>{u}n    
:{n}{k}{u}> <nn><s_1pl><o_sg>:>{u}>neen
:k{u}> <nn><s_2pl><o_sg>:>{u}>neewa
:w{u}> <nn><s_3pl><o_sg>:>{u}>neewa

