:k{u}> <aa><s_2pl><o_3sg>:>aawa
:w{u}> <aa><s_3pl><o_3sg>:>aawaawal
:w{u}> <aa><s_3pl><o_3sg>:>aawal

# Transitive Animate Verbs w/ Plural Object
